npm create vite@latest
npm i -D tailwindcss@3 postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwind init -p
on tailwind.config.js content add:
content: [
"./index.html",
"./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
],

routing:
npi i react-router-dom

connecting to backend:
we will now do it using first principles
later using react-hook-forms,react-query,swr for data fetching
